parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to serious injuries or fatalities in the event of a crash, as the airbags may not deploy or may deploy incorrectly.
symptoms: Airbags did not deploy in a crash
airbag warning light illuminated
horn malfunction
seatbelt pretensioner malfunction
loss of airbag and seatbelt deployment capability.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay or unavailability of recall repairs can lead to continued risk of injury or death due to the faulty airbag system.
symptoms: Notification of recall received
but parts are not available
dealer confirms parts are not available
manufacturer exceeds reasonable time for recall repair.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the occupant restraint controller can lead to the failure of the airbag system, resulting in serious injuries or fatalities in the event of a crash.
symptoms: Loss of airbag and seatbelt deployment capability
shorting condition resulting in negative voltage transient
occupant restraint controller malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the TIPM can cause the vehicle to shut down, leaving the driver stranded, and potentially leading to accidents or other safety risks.
symptoms: The vehicle shuts down
the battery needs to be tapped with a wire to start
the clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various issues, including faulty door locks, alarm malfunctions, and engine problems, which can lead to safety risks and inconvenience.
symptoms: The keypad to lock the doors doesn't work
the alarm goes off
the lock door button on the door doesn't work
the window buttons work
the car drags when accelerating
the check engine light and gas cap light come on
the mileage increases rapidly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine stalling can cause the vehicle to lose power and potentially lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The car stalls on the highway without warning
requiring towing to a repair shop.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Air Bag and Seat Belt Pretensioners Recall
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The potential loss of air bag and seat belt pretensioners deployment during a crash can increase the risk of injury or death.
symptoms: No symptoms mentioned
but the recall notice has been pending since September 2016 with no resolution.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Water/Moisture Accumulation in Tail Light Fixtures
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The accumulation of water/moisture in the tail light fixtures can cause electrical issues, leading to safety risks and potential accidents.
symptoms: Water/moisture accumulation in the tail light fixtures
causing the reverse light to malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission overheating can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents or stranding the driver. It can also lead to costly repairs and potentially cause damage to other components.
symptoms: The transmission overheating light comes on
the vehicle loses power
the vehicle cannot be driven more than a short distance without overheating.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Power Loss Due to Carburetor Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Sudden power loss can cause accidents, especially when driving at high speeds. It can also lead to costly repairs and potentially cause damage to other components.
symptoms: The vehicle suddenly loses power
the vehicle's speed drops significantly
the vehicle may stall or hesitate.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Roll-Away Incidents Due to Shifter Assembly Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Roll-away incidents can cause accidents, injuries, and damage to property. It can also lead to costly repairs and potentially cause damage to other components.
symptoms: The vehicle rolls away without warning
the vehicle moves without the driver's input
the shifter assembly fails to engage properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Ignition switch failure can cause the vehicle to roll away, leading to accidents, injuries, and damage to property. It can also lead to costly repairs and potentially cause damage to other components.
symptoms: The ignition key can be removed from any position
the vehicle can roll away without warning
the ignition switch fails to function properly.
